			<div class="description col three">
				<p><a href="./">Maquette: "Anti-Loitering Paint"</a></p>
				<p><em>2013 - Winter</em></p>
				<p><em class="background">&ndash; object, maquette, design, speculative, advertisement, fiction, research, smelly</em></p>
				<p>Design research meant to address the use of devices used to curb loitering in cities (e.g., spikes on benches, uneven surfaces): a durian-based paint that can thwart potential loiterers.</p>

<ul>
<li><p><strong>Skills:</strong>
Make a believable maquette, frame an issue with minimal context, imagine and iterate on fictional products and usage</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Tools:</strong>
Paint, woodshop</p></li>
</ul>

